data.description: Great potential 3 bed/2 1/2 bath investment property located on the #4 hole of the famed Robert Trent Jones golf course. Enjoy the higher ground (and cheaper insurance) in world-class Palmetto Dunes. Home to 3 miles of pristine beach, 3 incredible golf courses, tennis and pickleball along with great walkability to the fun and shopping at Shelter Cove, Palmetto Dunes has one of the longest short term rental markets in the country.  Make an offer on this fixer-upper priced below market!
